extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Anime Library], This library consists of details of diffrent anime .

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The anime library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Anime:] !{data.anime_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.availability_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.availability_finished_count}
      li #[strong Creators:] !{data.animeCreator_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}

